# SPA Routing Rules for Tamuu
# This file ensures that Cloudflare Pages serves the index.html for all sub-paths.

# 1. CATCH-ALL SPA RULE (MUST BE FIRST)
/*  /index.html  200

# 2. PROXIED ROUTES (Explicit for clarity)
/invitations  /index.html  200
/dashboard    /index.html  200
/upgrade      /index.html  200
/admin/*      /admin/:splat 200
